title: Titsiana Booberini
creator_credit: VCA Film and Television School, University of Melbourne and Robert Luketic
brief_description: Internationally acclaimed musical story starring Tania Lacy as the ugly duckling check-out chick with a facial hair problem and Sophie Lee as the supermarket bully. This graduating film was so successful at film festivals around the world that its director was courted by Hollywood and went on to direct the box office hit ‘Legally Blonde’ (2001).
